{
  "stem": "22447.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some-- [LAUGHS] some soldiers wasn't very good at aiming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't hit the target, so what they done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if you didn't get a certain score, you didn't get an extra sixpence, what they called proficiency pay.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So what they did, if nobody hit the target, they put a pencil through the target so when they checked, they said, yes, he's-- he's hit past it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you get your extra sixpence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You get your extra sixpence a day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, that was eight weeks in Hounslow Heath, then you joined the battalion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, that went down from February down through March.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went home for Passover March, April.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the other May we got posted to a battalion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, in between, the Dunkirk disaster cropped up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where we was supposed to be going to France, it got stopped because they were bringing the troops back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we got held-- I think it was in Stanmore we went.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we was waiting, nobody knew where-- where to go, whether to send them to France or not to send them because they were coming back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they didn't admit it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All they said was, everything is going according to plan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were coming back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we joined the battalion in a little town near Christchurch called Cattistock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never heard of it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think it's on the map, but they found these places in the Countess of Ilchester's state-- estate.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were put in the horse stables.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, they had horses in those days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were put n the stables and we joined the battalion, what remained of the battalion.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We made it up and said that we had nothing, just a-- a few rifles and some ammunition.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
